  Laverty
DÓMINE, qui dixísti: Nisi efficiámini sicut párvuli, non intrábitis in regnum cælórum: da nobis, quæsumus; ita sanctæ Terésiæ Vírginis in humilitáte et simplicitáte cordis vestígia sectári, ut præmia consequámur ætérna: Qui vivis.
O LORD, who hast said: Unless you become as little children you shall not enter the kingdom of heaven: grant unto us, we beseech thee, so to follow in humility and simplicity of heart the footsteps of saint Theresa the Virgin, that we may obtain everlasting rewards: Who livest.
